<!-- ============ INTRO ============ -->
<section class="intro">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="intro-grid">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span>The Studio</span>
        <h2 class="display" style="margin-top:24px;">A brand partner.<br/>A <em>considered</em> approach.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="body reveal delay-1">
        <p class="lede">
          Most agencies sell volume. We don’t. We work with a handful of clients at a time so every detail is treated like it matters — because it does.
        </p>
        <p>
          Behind every great-looking business is a system: a brand that says the right thing without saying too much, a website that quietly does the selling, content that compounds week over week. We design that system, then hand you the keys.
        </p>
        <div class="pill-row">
          <span class="pill">Strategy first</span>
          <span class="pill">Premium design</span>
          <span class="pill">Bilingual EN / ES</span>
          <span class="pill">One-on-one</span>
          <span class="pill">Built for growth</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ SERVICES ============ -->
<section class="services" id="services">
