        <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span>Why OliveBranch</span>
        <h2 class="display" style="margin-top:24px;">Why businesses choose <em>OliveBranch.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal delay-1">
        <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:22px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--charcoal);max-width:46ch;">
          We work with a small number of clients at a time so every detail is handled with care — the way premium businesses deserve.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="why-cards reveal delay-2">
      <div class="why-card">
        <span class="num">/ 01</span>
        <h3>Personalized One-on-One Service</h3>
        <p>You speak directly with the person designing your brand. No account managers, no handoffs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <span class="num">/ 02</span>
        <h3>Fast Communication</h3>
        <p>Replies within hours, not days. Clear timelines, weekly check-ins, no surprises.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <span class="num">/ 03</span>
        <h3>Modern Premium Design</h3>
        <p>Editorial-quality design that ages well — today's tools, timeless aesthetics.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <span class="num">/ 04</span>
        <h3>Bilingual English / Spanish Support</h3>
        <p>Full creative work, copywriting, and client conversations in both languages.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <span class="num">/ 05</span>
        <h3>Built for Growth</h3>
        <p>Every project includes the strategy and structure to keep paying off long after launch.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <span class="num">/ 06</span>
        <h3>Professional &amp; Reliable</h3>
        <p>Launches on schedule. Files organized. Easy to come back to a year from now.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

