<!-- ============ ABOUT ============ -->
<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="about-intro reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span>Our Values</span>
      <h2 class="display" style="margin-top:24px;">Growth, <em>with grace.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid about-grid--story">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="first">
          OliveBranch Marketing Haus was created to help businesses grow with purpose, strategy, and clarity.
        </p>
        <p>
          We believe premium design should feel personal and purposeful — that's what we want for the people we work with. A business that opens doors. A brand that says the right thing the first time. A marketing system you don't have to babysit.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal delay-1">
        <p>
          Our values are rooted in our faith in Jesus Christ. Everything we do in our business is for God's glory, and we strive to honor Him through integrity, excellence, and the way we serve others.
        </p>
        <p>
          We believe in having a personal relationship with Jesus, and that relationship guides how we love, lead, and work.
        </p>
        <p>
          The olive branch in our name is intentional: an old symbol for new beginnings, peace of mind, and steady, generational growth.
        </p>
        <p class="scripture">
          <em>"Let your light shine before others, that they may see your good deeds and glorify your Father in heaven"</em> <span class="ref">— Matthew 5:16</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="team-row team-row--single">
      <article class="team-card team-card--duo reveal">
        <div class="team-photo has-image" data-portrait="duo">
          <img class="team-photo-img" src="assets/founders.jpg" alt="Joshua Chavez and Valeria Castro-Chavez" />
          <span class="placeholder-meta">portrait · joshua &amp; valeria</span>
        </div>
        <div class="team-meta">
          <div class="duo-names">
            <div class="duo-person">
              <div class="team-name" data-name="founder">Joshua Chavez</div>
              <div class="team-role" data-role="founder">Founder · Creative Direction</div>
            </div>
            <div class="duo-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="duo-person">
